// TODO As a developer, I can verify that my application is stable and bug free.
// AC: The application is thoroughly tested using functional and unit tests.
// AC: Thorough unit tests are written using JUnit.

// TODO As a developer, I can deploy my application's front and backend code to a host.
// AC: Back end is deployed to a host such as Render.com.
// AC: Front end is deployed to a host such as Github pages.
// AC: Automating deployments is preffered.

// TODO As a developer, I must make significant and meaningful contributions to both the front and back end code on the project.


